Greenpeace UK activists protest at RAF (Royal Air Force) Mildenhall in Suffolk, as United States President Biden lands in the UK ahead of the G7 summit. Greenpeace is demanding urgent action on climate change, biodiversity loss and vaccines for developing countries.

title: Greenpeace - Protest at RAF Mildenhall as President Biden Lands in the UK
